snippet: But to some policy makers practiced in the art of compromise, preserving the power of the filibuster represented a potential missed opportunity.
abstract: Congressional Memo; some policy makers practiced in the art of compromise say Senate agreement to pull back from unilateral rules changes that would have eroded power of filibuster represents potential missed opportunity.
lead_paragraph: But to some policy makers practiced in the art of compromise, preserving the power of the filibuster represented a potential missed opportunity.

headline.main: Filibuster Deal Heralds Stirrings of Compromise
